Sentencas: First-principles supercell calculations of oxygen vacancies in the Ba0.5Sr0.5Co1-yFeyO3-delta (BSCF) perovskites are presented.
Titulo: First principles calculations of oxygen vacancy formation and migration in mixed conducting Ba0.5Sr0.5Co1-yFeyO3-δ perovskites

Sentencas: The density of states is determined for different iron content and oxygen vacancy concentrations, and the characteristic differences for Co and Fe are discussed.
Titulo: First principles calculations of oxygen vacancy formation and migration in mixed conducting Ba0.5Sr0.5Co1-yFeyO3-δ perovskites

Sentencas: We analyze the dependences of the defect (oxygen vacancy) formation and migration energies on the Fe content and compare the calculated properties with those of related LaCoO3 and LaFeO3 perovskites.
Titulo: First principles calculations of oxygen vacancy formation and migration in mixed conducting Ba0.5Sr0.5Co1-yFeyO3-δ perovskites
